data.value: Fairmont, Edwalton, Nottinghamshire,NG12 5EU Detached House | 5 Bed Fairmont can be found in the highly sought-after leafy suburban setting of Edwalton and affords a breath-taking level of luxury and contemporary quality from the moment you step through the door. Set back from the Melton Road, this home is secluded, private and discreetly accessed through a secure remote controlled gated entrance with a delightful backdrop of established and mature trees.

data.value: Peache, Bramcote, Nottinghamshire,NG9 3DX Detached House | 4 Bed This new-build detached house is situated in a highly sought after and regarded location within proximity to various local amenities,schools, and excellent transport links. This property has a contemporary design built around modern family living and boasts spacious accommodation spanning across three floors whilst being finished to an exceptional standard throughout. To the ground floor is an open plan high spec kitchen diner benefiting from a range of high-end integrated appliances and complete with a sitting area along with a separate utility room, a W/C and an additional reception room. The first floor offers a light and spacious living room with Aluminium bi-folding doors opening out to the rear garden along with a double bedroom, a single bedroom and a four-piece bathroom suite. To the second floor there are two further double bedrooms serviced by two modern en-suite bathrooms. Outside there is ample parking to the front and to the rear is a private enclosed low maintenance garden featuring a Porcelain patio area.
